==背景==
公投是由齊普拉斯在2015年6月27日凌晨宣布<ref name="Referendum announcement"/>離舉行日僅有短短8天，此決定事先並沒有告知{{link-en|歐元集團|Eurogroup}}<ref>{{Cite web|title = EU taken by surprise by Greek referendum|url = http://www.stuff.co.nz/world/europe/69776916/eu-taken-by-surprise-by-greek-referendum|website = Stuff|accessdate = 2015-07-10|date = 29 June 2015|archive-date = 2015-07-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150718100310/http://www.stuff.co.nz/world/europe/69776916/eu-taken-by-surprise-by-greek-referendum|dead-url = no}}</ref>；6月28日凌晨，議會投票決定是否同意政府提出的公投案，將接受紓困與否交由全民公投。結果有178名支持（包括激進左翼聯盟、[[独立希腊人|独立希腊人]]、[[金色黎明_(政党)|金色黎明]]），120名反對（包括其他黨派），與2名議員棄權，公投案成立<ref>{{cite news|last1=Traynor|first1=Ian|last2=Hooper|first2=John|title=Greek banks to stay closed on Monday|url=http://www.theguardian.com/business/2015/jun/28/greek-crisis-ecb-decide-emergency-funding|accessdate=6 July 2015|work=The Guardian|date=28 June 2015|archive-date=2015-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150704083224/http://www.theguardian.com/business/2015/jun/28/greek-crisis-ecb-decide-emergency-funding|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

